{"tid":860771,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲有頭皮問題？","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T04:05:39.000Z","uid":167629,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d4ec5b1d5bb93f2f95559942bb0fb210116dac","tid":860771,"uid":167629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"首先唔係幾日無洗頭所以好多頭皮問題果隻<br />\n小弟平日本身都沖2次涼 朝早一次夜晚一次<br />\n每次都摔幾次頭先沖水<br />\n但明明洗到咁掃一掃啲頭髮都好似落雪咁細細粒又勁多<br />\n另一半好幾次忍唔住問我係咪懶得濟無洗頭<br />\n我好無奈次次都同佢講我其實日日都洗2次<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想根治呢個問題 有無解決方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6a4dca22cfe5d49497baba9b37ef4b4ed60f57","tid":860771,"uid":167629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95b7ee9ec6f2620fa7a33f6eaed3a49304215ab","tid":860771,"uid":215504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"可能洗得太多搞到頭皮乾燥所以多頭皮？<br />\n我兩日洗一次都無咩頭皮"},{"pid":"bf13792471770a6f4cd71253b875ab2deda8e938","tid":860771,"uid":167629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f95b7ee9ec6f2620fa7a33f6eaed3a49304215ab","tid":860771,"uid":215504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"可能洗得太多搞到頭皮乾燥所以多頭皮？<br />\n我兩日洗一次都無咩頭皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:27:16.000Z","msg":"試過有排2日洗一次 情況一樣<br />\n同埋我一唔洗頭第二朝成個頭會飛起晒成個悟空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863099ae9b0f13ecd46ded1cf6c944f24e895a68","tid":860771,"uid":180402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"有冇試過自己轉下用唔同洗頭水<br />\n一係就去睇醫生 <br />\n會介紹d藥用洗頭水比你"},{"pid":"c35e4fa0c22233c4efc7dd3e4cc5fc2e21a446e5","tid":860771,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c